- Use mobile-first approach
- Implement proper breakpoints
- Use relative units
- Test across devices
- Handle orientation changes

## Layout
- Use proper layout systems
- Implement proper grid
- Use flexbox appropriately
- Handle overflow properly
- Maintain proper spacing

## Typography
- Use proper font scale
- Implement proper line heights
- Use proper font weights
- Maintain readability
- Handle font loading

## Colors
- Use proper color system
- Implement proper contrast
- Use semantic colors
- Handle dark mode
